pqlite3 (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of PQLite - Post-Quantum SQLite
  * ML-KEM-768 key encapsulation (FIPS 203) via liboqs
  * AES-256-GCM transparent page encryption
  * ML-DSA-65 digital signatures (FIPS 204)
  * Column-level encryption, audit logging, data masking
  * Row-level security, FIPS 140-3 mode, encrypted backups
  * Based on SQLite 3.53.0

 -- Dyber, Inc. <engineering@dyber.io>  Mon, 31 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000
